ates and Russia, we consider China, Japan, the leading European powers and countries of the Asia-Pacific region. Globalization has brought changes in the concept of bilateral and multilateral relations of the states of the world. The activities of fundamentalist and extremist Islamic organizations create more and more hotbeds of tension in different parts of the world. There are serious security threats existing in the region of Central Asia.','1',false,false,false,false)
