aking political scientist is especially important, each time creating a new unique work of art of impact on the audience. Making decisions in the conditions of lack of information, and in some cases due to lack of time, a person replaces the process of building a complex and in-depth portrait of a person by creating his image - a symbolic substitute that reflects and projects his main features. Depending on the specific purpose, different features can be projected.','1',false,false,false,false)
