nd database applications, and data preprocessing with pandas and numpy. Additionally, this course provides students understanding of using non-strict types of variables. Finally, students will be developing a web application on Django framework. Upon completion, students should be able to code using PEP8 standard, create, test and debug fully functional and complicated applications on Python programming language.','1',false,false,false,false)
