al knowledge of the disciplines of the specialty; mastering practical skills, technology work in the specialty directly in the workplace using a PC, modern software and modern office equipment; the study and analysis of the real situation in the statics and dynamics of CAD in the short and long term with respect to the company - the base of internship; evaluation of the achieved commercial results of automation implementation in the short and long term, in relation to these specific enterprises; familiarity with the technology and technology of CAD development, procedures for making and implementing automation solutions at specific enterprises; collecting material for the graduation projects.','1',false,false,false,true)
