view - every person during the day at the subconscious level repeatedly solves this problem by moving: - from home to work and back; - from work to the theater, to the cinema, to a cafe, etc .; - in the dining room during lunch, in rooms and institutions during work, etc. - even the primitive man during the hunt, solved this problem in the process of chasing the prey! In his social and practical activities, a person also daily solves the problems of logistics of optimal movement: - cargo; - troops; - finished products and components in the process of its production; - passengers and much more. Logistics - as science is known since Roman times, where: “Logist” is a supplier in the army. \"','1',false,false,false,false)
