nary training program covering the elements of mathematical analysis, modern statistical methods and equations of mathematical physics, problems of thermoelasticity, which deepen the mathematical understanding of physical problems and develops logical and algorithmic thinking skills. The course provides students with mathematical tools and mastering special software (MatLab, Simulink), which should be used in physical problems, modern methods of studying and solving mathematical problems.','1',false,false,false,false)
