ntrollers, devices and I/o interfaces of the built-in system. Algorithms of functioning of basic elements and the basic schemes of their inclusion, and also their Association as a part of devices and systems are investigated. The differences between Android, Linux and Windows CE platforms and the main ways to boot the embedded system are described. The principles of organization of built-in systems and interaction of their components are given. The basics of programming embedded systems.','1',false,false,false,false)
