output interfaces of the embedded system. The algorithms of functioning of the basic elements and the basic schemes of their inclusion, as well as their combination in the composition of devices and systems, are investigated. It describes the differences between the Android, Linux and Windows CE platforms and the main ways to boot an embedded system. The principles of the organization of embedded systems and the interaction of their components are given. The basics of programming embedded systems are considered.','1',false,false,false,false)
