 beginning of the course, an overview of the main trends in the development of infrastructure solutions, which led to the emergence of the concept of cloud computing, is given. Attention is paid to virtualization technologies. The course further covers the main models for providing cloud computing services. Reviews of leading vendors are reviewed.\"','1',false,false,false,false)
