заций для ВС как с общей, так и распределенной памятью (в том числе, многоядерных и кластерных архитектур).','The use of parallel programming for the organization of high-performance computing leads to a number of specific problems, moreover, the architecture of a parallel computing system involves different methods and means of solving them, and practical language implementations provide the programmer with specific tools for writing effective programs. The discipline \"Architectures of computing systems and problems of parallel programming\" is designed to study the tools and methods of creating applications for different architectures of the aircraft. The main attention in the study of the discipline is paid to the practical skills of writing parallel programs in terms of specific libraries and/or language implementations for the sun with both General and distributed memory (including multicore and cluster architectures).','1',false,false,false,false)
