he training of students to expand knowledge in the use of databases in different areas of activity, based on the use of a systematic approach to the analysis of information, to get acquainted with the basic concepts in the field of analytical processing of big data, provides the ability to analyze and solve problems in practice and research activities in the context of the development of science and changing social practices, forms the ability to acquire new knowledge. As a result of studying the discipline students receive knowledge forming a system of concepts of modern information technology.','1',false,false,false,false)
