et), a frame model, a logical model, a semantic network. Also considers the basics of neural networks, genetic algorithms, evolutionary algorithms. On practical classes: development of a program for the implementation of direct inference in the production model and the model of knowledge representation in a specific area of ​​knowledge.','6',false,false,false,false)
