th study of the scientific and psychological-pedagogical foundations of the structure and content of the course of informatics in secondary schools, understanding the methodological ideas embodied in them the ability to solve the problems of teaching informatics for scientific activity by a schoolchild, the formation of skills for an independent learning process ological work. The program is intended to provide theoretical and practical teacher training in the field of informatics teaching methods.','1',false,false,false,false)
