 of data analysis and processing, studying the questions of planning and organizing an experiment, studying ways of mathematical processing of measurement results, the study of methods for carrying out scientific research, the study of methodologies of theoretical and experimental research second, the analysis of theoretical and experimental research and the formulation of conclusions and recommendations.','2',false,false,false,false)
