rovides a detailed overview and description of the most important security methods and models, as well as practical problems solved in the field of information security. To this end, the implementation of system audit is carried out using various systems and development environments. Innovative engineering projects are being carried out for the development of software for various purposes using modern design methods and the implementation of protection and safety management systems is being implemented. In the process of educational activity, software implementation of various EDS algorithms and electronic payment systems is carried out in order to solve practical various tasks.','2',false,false,false,false)
