ими сетями. Для этого осуществляется реализация нейронных сетей, используя среду MATLAB.','The principles of the construction of neural networks, types of neural networks and application in various tasks are given knowledge in the field of modern models of artificial neural networks, methods of their application for solving practical problems. We consider ways to implement innovative engineering projects for the development of software for various purposes using neural networks and modern design methods and best practices. Tasks are considered and algorithms for their solution are developed for the implementation of software implementations of neural networks with the aim of solving practical various tasks. This discipline provides a detailed overview and description of the most important methods of teaching neural networks of various structures, as well as practical problems solved by these networks. To this end, neural networks are implemented using the MATLAB environment.','2',false,false,false,false)
